sée avec documentation intégrée.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Consultations Texte</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Gérez les questions patients asynchrones et les suivis.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clipboard-list h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="8" height="4" x="8" y="2" rx="1" ry="1"></rect><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="M12 11h4"></path><path d="M12 16h4"></path><path d="M8 11h.01"></path><path d="M8 16h.01"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Support de Visite en Personne</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Consultez les plannings, historiques et finalisez les notes à la clinique.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.